{"tid":28704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆料] 高登五毛根本就係ADMIN之一","createTime":"2016-12-08T06:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T06:12:00.000Z","uid":4493,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c038f95a768c0b9c8f6db7a2a7b95e7a9fc35a3","tid":28704,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">華山派麻鬼鬼</span>大家應該都見慣啦<br />\n有時扮假膠 有時扮熱狗 間中扮青政<br />\n最鍾意挑起兩邊鬥爭<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢個分身撩陰腿 之前半夜三點都會準時合作互推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過見佢換錯分身幾次 亦都冇被bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但除此之外 最唔尋常嘅就係佢每日貼文數目<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pib8Hre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpib8Hre.jpg&h=ab448d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平常人根本冇可能有時間同埋精力開咁多個主題 所以基本上已經可以肯定佢係職業會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最出奇嘅係一個冚家剷五毛 竟然在高登官方Facebook多次被精選 話佢同林早洩無關係都無人信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T542jh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT542jh4.jpg&h=369fbb46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M49id1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM49id1R.jpg&h=306194c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/140426_a252f850bfd312d63af8ab9ec229f173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F140426_a252f850bfd312d63af8ab9ec229f173.jpg&h=2148df3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有新發現會繼續爆料 開明自由嘅LIHK萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d699ed999e59c918762c935a5902ffedf52600","tid":28704,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"仲係CK fans#<img src=\"/assets/face